                      size: 16,
                      color: theme.textTheme.bodySmall?.color ??
                          const Color(0xFF6B7280),
                    ),
                    const SizedBox(width: 8),
                    Text(
                      task.type,
                      style: TextStyle(
                        fontSize: 13,
                        fontWeight: FontWeight.w500,
                        color: theme.textTheme.bodySmall?.color ??
                            const Color(0xFF6B7280),
                      ),
                    ),
                    const SizedBox(width: 8),
                    Container(
                      padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(
                          horizontal: 8, vertical: 2),
                      decoration: BoxDecoration(
                        color: getStatusBgColor(task.status, isDark),
                        borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(12),
                      ),
                      child: Text(
                        getStatusText(task.status),
                        style: TextStyle(
                          fontSize: 11,
                          fontWeight: FontWeight.w500,
                          color: getStatusTextColor(task.status, isDark),
                        ),
                      ),
                    ),
                  ],
                ),
                if (task.status == TaskStatus.generated ||
                    task.status == TaskStatus.failed)
                  GestureDetector(
                    onTap: () => deleteTask(task.id),
                    child: Container(
                      padding: const EdgeInsets.all(4),
                      decoration: BoxDecoration(
                        borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(20),
                      ),
                      child: Icon(
                        LucideIcons.x,
                        size: 16,
                        color: theme.textTheme.bodySmall?.color ??
                            const Color(0xFF8E8E93),
                      ),
                    ),
                  ),
              ],
            ),
          ),

          if (task.isExpanded) ...[
            const SizedBox(height: 12),

            // 任务参数
            if (task.parameters.isNotEmpty)
              Padding(
                padding: const EdgeInsets.only(bottom: 12),
                child: Column(
                  children: task.parameters.map((param) {
                    return Padding(
                      padding: const EdgeInsets.only(bottom: 8),
                      child: Row(
                        crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.start,
                        children: [
                          SizedBox(
                            width: 80,
                            child: Padding(
                              padding: const EdgeInsets.only(top: 10),
                              child: Text(
                                '${param.key}：',
                                style: TextStyle(
                                  fontSize: 13,
                                  color: theme.textTheme.bodySmall?.color ??
                                      const Color(0xFF8E8E93),
                                ),
                              ),
                            ),
                          ),
                          Expanded(
                            child: _buildParamInput(task, param, theme, isDark),
                          ),
                        ],
                      ),
                    );
                  }).toList(),
                ),
              ),

            // 操作按钮
            if (task.status == TaskStatus.generated ||
                task.status == TaskStatus.failed)
              _buildActionButtons(task, theme, isDark),

            if (task.status == TaskStatus.executing) _buildExecutingIndicator(),

            if (task.status == TaskStatus.completed) _buildCompletedIndicator(),
          ],
        ],
      ),
    );
  }

  // 构建参数输入框（支持下拉、日期或文本）
  Widget _buildParamInput(
      Task task, TaskParam param, ThemeData theme, bool isDark) {
    // 只有在 generated 状态下可以编辑参数，并且当前处于编辑模式
    bool canEdit = (task.status == TaskStatus.generated ||
            task.status == TaskStatus.failed) &&
        editingTaskId == task.id;

    final inputFillColor =
        isDark ? const Color(0xFF374151) : const Color(0xFFF9FAFB);
    final inputBorderColor =
        isDark ? const Color(0xFF4B5563) : const Color(0xFFE5E7EB);
    final textColor =
        theme.textTheme.bodyMedium?.color ?? const Color(0xFF1C1C1E);

    // 检查是否为日期或时间参数
    final lowerKey = param.key.toLowerCase();

    // 1. 优先判断是否为日期+时间 (DateTime)
    final isDateTimeParam = lowerKey.contains('datetime') ||
        lowerKey.contains('timestamp') ||
        (lowerKey.contains('date') && lowerKey.contains('time')) ||
        lowerKey.contains('修改时间') ||
        lowerKey.contains('完整时间');

    // 2. 判断是否为时间 (Time)
    final isTimeParam = !isDateTimeParam &&
        (lowerKey.contains('time') || lowerKey.contains('时间'));

    // 3. 判断是否为日期 (Date)
    final isDateParam = !isDateTimeParam &&
        !isTimeParam &&
        (lowerKey.contains('date') ||
            lowerKey.contains('day') ||
            lowerKey.contains('deadline') ||
            lowerKey.contains('schedule') ||
            lowerKey.contains('start') ||
            lowerKey.contains('end') ||
            lowerKey.contains('birth') ||
            lowerKey.contains('日期') ||
            lowerKey.contains('天') ||
            lowerKey.contains('生日') ||
            lowerKey.contains('截止') ||
            lowerKey.contains('开始') ||
            lowerKey.contains('结束') ||
            RegExp(r'^\d{4}[-/]\d{1,2}[-/]\d{1,2}$').hasMatch(param.value));

    if (canEdit && (isDateParam || isTimeParam || isDateTimeParam)) {
      return GestureDetector(
        onTap: () async {
          DateTime initialDate = DateTime.now();
          if (isTimeParam) {
            // 尝试解析时间 (优先完整格式，失败尝试 HH:mm)
            try {
              initialDate =
                  DateFormat('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss').parse(param.value);
            } catch (_) {
              try {
                // 尝试解析 HH:mm，补全为当天
                final now = DateTime.now();
                final timeParts = param.value.split(':');
                if (timeParts.length >= 2) {
                  initialDate = DateTime(
                    now.year,
                    now.month,
                    now.day,
                    int.parse(timeParts[0]),
                    int.parse(timeParts[1]),
                  );
                }
              } catch (_) {}
            }
          } else if (isDateTimeParam) {
            // 解析日期时间 YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss
            try {
              initialDate =
                  DateFormat('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss').parse(param.value);
            } catch (_) {
              try {
                // 尝试不带秒的格式
                initialDate = DateFormat('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm').parse(param.value);
              } catch (__) {}
            }
          } else {
            // 解析日期 YYYY-MM-DD
            try {
              initialDate = DateFormat('yyyy-MM-dd').parse(param.value);
            } catch (_) {}
          }

          // 使用 CupertinoDatePicker 实现手机端滚轮风格
          DateTime tempPickedDate = initialDate;
          await showCupertinoModalPopup<void>(
            context: context,
            builder: (BuildContext context) {
              return Container(
                height: 280,
                color: theme.scaffoldBackgroundColor,
                child: Column(
                  children: [
                    // Toolbar
                    Container(
                      height: 44,
                      decoration: BoxDecoration(
                        color: theme.cardTheme.color,
                        border: Border(
                          bottom: BorderSide(
                            color: theme.dividerTheme.color ??
                                Colors.grey.withOpacity(0.2),
                            width: 0.5,
                          ),
                        ),
                      ),
                      child: Row(
                        mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.spaceBetween,
                        children: [
                          CupertinoButton(
                            padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 16),
                            child: const Text('取消',
                                style: TextStyle(fontSize: 14)),
                            onPressed: () => Navigator.of(context).pop(),
                          ),
                          CupertinoButton(
                            padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 16),
                            child: const Text('确定',
                                style: TextStyle(
                                    fontSize: 14, fontWeight: FontWeight.bold)),
                            onPressed: () {
                              // 校验开始/结束时间
                              // ... (校验逻辑略，如果需要可以保留或扩展)

                              setState(() {
                                if (isTimeParam || isDateTimeParam) {
                                  param.value =
                                      DateFormat('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')
                                          .format(tempPickedDate);
                                } else {
                                  param.value = DateFormat('yyyy-MM-dd')
                                      .format(tempPickedDate);
                                }
                              });
                              Navigator.of(context).pop();
                            },
                          ),
                        ],
                      ),
                    ),
                    // Picker
                    Expanded(
                      child: CupertinoDatePicker(
                        mode: (isDateTimeParam || isTimeParam)
                            ? CupertinoDatePickerMode.dateAndTime
                            : CupertinoDatePickerMode.date,
                        initialDateTime: initialDate,
                        minimumDate: DateTime(2000),
                        maximumDate: DateTime(2100),
                        use24hFormat: true,
                        onDateTimeChanged: (DateTime newDate) {
                          tempPickedDate = newDate;
                        },
                      ),
                    ),
                  ],
                ),
              );
            },
          );
        },
        child: Container(
          padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 12, vertical: 10),
          decoration: BoxDecoration(
            color: inputFillColor,
            borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(8),
            border: Border.all(color: inputBorderColor),
          ),
          child: Row(
            mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.spaceBetween,
            children: [
              Text(
                param.value.isEmpty
                    ? ((isDateTimeParam || isTimeParam) ? '选择日期时间' : '选择日期')
                    : param.value,
                style: TextStyle(fontSize: 13, color: textColor),
              ),
              Icon(isTimeParam ? LucideIcons.clock : LucideIcons.calendar,
                  size: 16, color: textColor.withOpacity(0.6)),
            ],
          ),
        ),
      );
    }

    // 普通文本输入 + 选项 Chips (合并显示)
    if (canEdit) {
      final controller = _paramControllers['${task.id}_${param.key}'];

      return Column(
        crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.start,
        children: [
          // 输入框
          TextFormField(
            controller: controller, // 使用 State 中管理的 Controller
            style: TextStyle(fontSize: 13, color: textColor),
            decoration: InputDecoration(
              isDense: true,
              contentPadding:
                  const EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 12, vertical: 10),
              fillColor: inputFillColor,
              filled: true,
              border: OutlineInputBorder(
                borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(8),
                borderSide: BorderSide(color: inputBorderColor),
              ),
              enabledBorder: OutlineInputBorder(
                borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(8),
                borderSide: BorderSide(color: inputBorderColor),
              ),
            ),
            onChanged: (val) {
              param.value = val;
            },
          ),

          // 选项 Chips (如果存在)
          if (param.options != null && param.options!.isNotEmpty)
            Padding(
              padding: const EdgeInsets.only(top: 8),
              child: Wrap(
                spacing: 8,
                runSpacing: 8,
                children: param.options!.map((option) {
                  final isSelected = param.value == option;
                  return GestureDetector(
                    onTap: () {
                      setState(() {
                        param.value = option;
                        controller?.text = option; // 同步更新输入框
                      });
                    },
                    child: Container(
                      padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(
                          horizontal: 12, vertical: 6),
                      decoration: BoxDecoration(
                        color: isSelected
                            ? const Color(0xFF007AFF)
                            : inputFillColor,
                        borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(16),
                        border: Border.all(
                          color: isSelected
                              ? const Color(0xFF007AFF)
                              : inputBorderColor,
                        ),
                      ),
                      child: Text(
                        option,
                        style: TextStyle(
                          fontSize: 13,
                          color: isSelected ? Colors.white : textColor,
                        ),
                      ),
                    ),
                  );
                }).toList(),
              ),
            ),
        ],
      );
    }

    return Padding(
      padding: const EdgeInsets.only(top: 10),
      child: Text(
        param.value,
        style: TextStyle(
          fontSize: 13,
          color: textColor,
        ),
      ),
    );
  }

  Widget _buildActionButtons(Task task, ThemeData theme, bool isDark) {
    if (editingTaskId == task.id) {
      return Row(
        children: [
          Expanded(
            child: GestureDetector(
              onTap: () => saveEdit(task.id),
              child: Container(
                padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 10),
                decoration: BoxDecoration(
                  color: const Color(0xFF007AFF),
                  borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(8),
                ),
                child: const Center(
                  child: Text(
                    '保存',
                    style: TextStyle(
                      fontSize: 15,
                      fontWeight: FontWeight.w500,
                      color: Colors.white,
                    ),
                  ),
                ),
              ),
            ),
          ),
          const SizedBox(width: 8),
          Expanded(
            child: GestureDetector(
              onTap: cancelEdit,
              child: Container(
                padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 10),
                decoration: BoxDecoration(
                  color: isDark
                      ? const Color(0xFF374151)
                      : const Color(0xFFF2F2F7),
                  borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(8),
                ),
                child: Center(
                  child: Text(
                    '取消',
                    style: TextStyle(
                      fontSize: 15,
                      fontWeight: FontWeight.w500,
                      color: theme.textTheme.bodyMedium?.color ??
                          const Color(0xFF3C3C43),
                    ),
                  ),
                ),
              ),
            ),
          ),
        ],
      );
    }

    return Row(
      children: [
        Expanded(
          child: GestureDetector(
            onTap: () => startEditTask(task),
            child: Container(
              padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 10),
              decoration: BoxDecoration(
                color:
                    isDark ? const Color(0xFF374151) : const Color(0xFFF2F2F7),
                borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(8),
              ),
              child: Center(
                child: Text(
                  '修正内容',
                  style: TextStyle(
                    fontSize: 15,
                    fontWeight: FontWeight.w500,
                    color: theme.textTheme.bodyMedium?.color ??
                        const Color(0xFF3C3C43),
                  ),
                ),
              ),
            ),
          ),
        ),
        const SizedBox(width: 8),
        Expanded(
          child: GestureDetector(
            onTap: () => executeTask(task.id),
            child: Container(
              padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 10),
              decoration: BoxDecoration(
                color: const Color(0xFF007AFF),
                borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(8),
              ),
              child: const Center(
                child: Text(
                  '确认执行',
                  style: TextStyle(
                    fontSize: 15,
                    fontWeight: FontWeight.w500,
                    color: Colors.white,
                  ),
                ),
              ),
            ),
          ),
        ),
      ],
    );
  }

  Widget _buildExecutingIndicator() {
    return Padding(
      padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 8),
      child: Row(
        mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.center,
        children: List.generate(3, (index) {
          return AnimatedBuilder(
            animation: _bounceController,
            builder: (context, child) {
              final delay = index * 0.15;
              final value =
                  ((_bounceController.value + delay) % 1.0 * 2 - 1).abs();
              return Container(
                margin: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 2),
                child: Transform.translate(
                  offset: Offset(0, -4 * (1 - value)),
                  child: Container(
                    width: 8,
                    height: 8,
                    decoration: BoxDecoration(
                      color: const Color(0xFF9333EA),
                      borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(4),
                    ),
                  ),
                ),
              );
            },
          );
        }),
      ),
    );
  }

  Widget _buildCompletedIndicator() {
    return const Padding(
      padding: EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: 8),
      child: Center(
        child: Text(
          '✓ 任务执行完成',
          style: TextStyle(
            fontSize: 14,
            color: Color(0xFF16A34A),
          ),
        ),
      ),
    );
  }

  Widget _buildRecordButton(bool isDark) {
    return Container(
      padding: EdgeInsets.only(
        left: 16,
        right: 16,
        top: 8,
        bottom: MediaQuery.of(context).padding.bottom + 16,
      ),
      child: Column(
        children: [
          // 录音时的取消提示区
          SizedBox(
            height: 40,
            child: isRecording
                ? AnimatedOpacity(
                    opacity: isRecording ? 1.0 : 0.0,
                    duration: const Duration(milliseconds: 200),
                    child: Row(
                      mainAxisAlignment: MainAxisAlignment.center,
                      children: [
                        Icon(
                          _isCanceling
                              ? LucideIcons.trash2
                              : LucideIcons.chevronUp,
                          size: 16,
                          color: _isCanceling
                              ? const Color(0xFFEF4444)
                              : (isDark
                                  ? const Color(0xFF9CA3AF)
                                  : const Color(0xFF8E8E93)),
                        ),
                        const SizedBox(width: 6),
                        Text(
                          _isCanceling ? '松开这里取消' : '手指上滑，取消发送',
                          style: TextStyle(
                            fontSize: 14,
                            fontWeight: FontWeight.w500,
                            color: _isCanceling
                                ? const Color(0xFFEF4444)
                                : (isDark
                                    ? const Color(0xFF9CA3AF)
                                    : const Color(0xFF8E8E93)),
                          ),
                        ),
                      ],
                    ),
                  )
                : null,
          ),
          const SizedBox(height: 8),
          GestureDetector(
            onPanDown: (_) {
              _isTouching = true;
              handleTouchStart();
            },
            onPanUpdate: (details) {
              if (!_isTouching) return;
              // 向上滑动超过一定距离触发取消状态
              if (details.localPosition.dy < -60) {
                if (!_isCanceling) setState(() => _isCanceling = true);
              } else {
                if (_isCanceling) setState(() => _isCanceling = false);
              }
            },
            onPanEnd: (_) {
              _isTouching = false;
              if (_isCanceling) {
                _cancelRecording();
              } else {
                handleTouchEnd();
              }
            },
            onPanCancel: () {
              _isTouching = false;
              _cancelRecording();
            },
            child: AnimatedContainer(
              duration: const Duration(milliseconds: 150),
              width: 64,
              height: 64,
              transform: Matrix4.identity()..scale(isRecording ? 1.1 : 1.0),
              transformAlignment: Alignment.center,
              decoration: BoxDecoration(
                color: _isCanceling
                    ? const Color(0xFF9CA3AF)
                    : isRecording
                        ? const Color(0xFFEF4444)
                        : const Color(0xFF007AFF),
                borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(32),
                boxShadow: [
                  BoxShadow(
                    color: (_isCanceling
                            ? const Color(0xFF9CA3AF)
                            : isRecording
                                ? const Color(0xFFEF4444)
                                : const Color(0xFF007AFF))
                        .withOpacity(0.4),
                    blurRadius: 24,
                    offset: const Offset(0, 8),
                  ),
                ],
              ),
              child: Center(
                child: Icon(
                  _isCanceling ? LucideIcons.trash2 : LucideIcons.mic,
                  size: 32,
                  color: Colors.white,
                ),
              ),
            ),
          ),
          const SizedBox(height: 8),
          Text(
            isRecording ? '正在录音...' : '按住说话',
            style: TextStyle(
              fontSize: 13,
              color: isDark ? const Color(0xFF9CA3AF) : const Color(0xFF8E8E93),
            ),
          ),
        ],
      ),
    );
  }
}

class StarPainter extends CustomPainter {
  final Color color;
  StarPainter({required this.color});

  @override
  void paint(Canvas canvas, Size size) {
    final paint = Paint()
      ..color = color
      ..style = PaintingStyle.fill;

    final path = Path();
    // SVG ViewBox is 24x24
    final scaleX = size.width / 24.0;
    final scaleY = size.height / 24.0;

    path.moveTo(12 * scaleX, 2 * scaleY);
    path.lineTo(14.39 * scaleX, 9.61 * scaleY);
    path.lineTo(22 * scaleX, 12 * scaleY);
    path.lineTo(14.39 * scaleX, 14.39 * scaleY);
    path.lineTo(12 * scaleX, 22 * scaleY);
    path.lineTo(9.61 * scaleX, 14.39 * scaleY);
    path.lineTo(2 * scaleX, 12 * scaleY);
    path.lineTo(9.61 * scaleX, 9.61 * scaleY);
    path.close();

    canvas.drawPath(path, paint);
  }

  @override
  bool shouldRepaint(covariant StarPainter oldDelegate) =>
      oldDelegate.color != color;
}
